# ‚ĖĄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĎ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ

# Mute volume
XF86AudioMute
	pulsemixer --toggle-mute

# Raise volume
XF86AudioRaiseVolume
	pulsemixer --change-volume +5

# Lower volume
XF86AudioLowerVolume
	pulsemixer --change-volume -5

# Media {next,previous}
XF86Audio{Next,Prev}
	mpc {next,prev}

# Media pause
XF86Audio{Pause}
	mpc {pause}

# Select Monitor
super + F3
	displayselect

# Clipboard
F7
  clipmenu -bw 2 -i -W 290 -X 1061 -Y 15 -l 15

# Screenshot tool
Print
  maimpick

# ScreenRecord tool
super + Print
  dmenurecord

# Stop screen-recording
super + Delete
  dmenurecord kill

# Lower brightness
XF86MonBrightnessDown
  brightnessctl set 500-

# Raise brightness
XF86MonBrightnessUp
  brightnessctl set +500

# Nerd Font selector
super + grave
  dmenunerdfont

# Move window to a new workspace
super + {_,shift + }{1-9,0}
	bspc {desktop -f,node -d} ^{1-9,10}

# System menu
super + BackSpace
  sysact

# Toggle current/previous workspace
super + {Tab,backslash}
  bspc desktop last --focus

# Close window
super + {_,shift + }q
	bspc node -{c,k}

# Open Browser
super + w
  librewolf

# Open lf
super + r
  kitty lf

# Open htop
super + shift + r
  kitty htop

# Toggle tiling/monocle
super + t
  bspc desktop -l next

# Rotate windows
super + y
	bspc node @focused:/ -R 90

# Focus {previous,next} window
super + {i,o}
	bspc node -f {prev,next}.local

# Pause media
super + p
  mpc toggle

# Pasue all media
super + shift + p
  mpc pause ; pauseallmpv

# Seek -10 seconds
super + bracketleft
  mpc seek -10

# Seek -60 seconds
super + shift + bracketleft
  mpc seek -60

# Seek +!0 seconds
super + bracketright
  mpc seek +10

# Seek +60 seconds
super + shift + bracketright
  mpc seek +60

# Open dmenu_hub
super + a
  dmenu_hub

# Open dmenu_hub
ctrl + space
  opener

# Open dmenu_run
super + d
  dmenu_run -bw 2 -i -W 390 -X 961 -Y 15 -l 15 -g 3

# Toggle gaps
super + shift + d
	bspc config window_gap {0,5}

# Resize outwards
super + {h,j,k,l}
	bspc node -z {left -20 0,bottom 0 20,top 0 -20,right 20 0}

# Resize inwards
super + shift + {h,j,k,l}
	bspc node -z {right -20 0,top 0 20,bottom 0 -20,left 20 0}

# Scratchpad calculator
super + apostrophe
  tdrop -a -w 50% -h 30% -y 4% -x 25% qalculate-gtk

# Terminal
super + Return
  kitty

# Scratchpad Terminal
super + shift + Return
  tdrop -a -w 65% -h 60% -y 4% -x 17% st -c spterm

# Increase or decrease gaps
super { ,+ shift }+ z
	bspc config window_gap $(($(bspc config window_gap) {+,-} 3))

# Open nmtui
super + c
  st -c nmtui -g=54x28 -e nmtui

# Toggle polybar
super + b
  sh ~/.config/bspwm/polybar/scripts/toggle.sh

# Add web bookmark
super + shift + b
  dmenu_web --add

# Open VimWiki
super + n
  kitty nvim -c VimwikiIndex

# Open Newsboat
super + shift + n
  kitty newsboat

# Open music player
super + m
  tdrop -a -w 65% -h 60% -y 4% -x 17% st -c spmusic -e ncmpcpp

# Mute volume
super + shift + m
  pulsemixer --toggle-mute

# Previous song
super + comma
  mpc prev

# Next song
super + period
  mpc next

# Repeat song
super + shift + period
 mpc repeat

# Swap current and largest window
super + space
	bspc node -s biggest.local || bspc node -s next.local

# Toggle window floating
super + shift + space
	bspc node focused -t \~floating

# Preselect ratio
super + ctrl + {1-9}
	bspc node -o 0.{1-9}

# Cancel preselection
super + ctrl + space
	bspc node -p cancel

# Web Search
alt + space
	dmenu_web

# Web Search
XF86Search
	dmenu_web

# Move Floating window {left,down,up,right}
super + {Left,Down,Up,Right}
	bspc node -v {-20 0,0 20,0 -20,20 0}
